data.name: Xslt_DocumentMergeImport
data.value:
<xsl:stylesheet version="1.0" xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" xmlns:arasx="http://www.aras.com/XsltExtensions/1.0" xmlns:msxsl="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:xslt" extension-element-prefixes="arasx msxsl"> <xsl:output method="xml" omit-xml-declaration="yes" standalone="yes" indent="yes"></xsl:output>
<xsl:template match="table"> <xsl:variable name="unique-files" select="arasx:GetUniqueFiles(row/path)" />
<xsl:variable name="file-query"> <Item type="File" action="get" select="id,checksum,file_size"> <xsl:attribute name="where"> <xsl:for-each select="$unique-files/Result/Item"> <xsl:if test="position() != 1"> OR </xsl:if> <xsl:text>([File].[checksum] = '</xsl:text> <xsl:value-of select="checksum" /> <xsl:text>' AND [File].[file_size] = </xsl:text> <xsl:value-of select="size" /> <xsl:text>)</xsl:text> </xsl:for-each> </xsl:attribute> </Item> </xsl:variable>
<xsl:variable name="existing-files" select="arasx:CallAction('ApplyItem',$file-query)//*[Item][1]" />
<xsl:variable name="unique-existing-files"> <Result> <xsl:for-each select="$unique-files/Result/Item"> <xsl:variable name="existing-file" select="$existing-files/Item[checksum = current()/checksum and file_size = current()/size][1]" /> <xsl:choose> <!-- use the existing file --> <xsl:when test="$existing-file"> <Item action="get"> <xsl:copy-of select="$existing-file/@*" /> <xsl:copy-of select="paths" /> </Item> </xsl:when> <!-- Upload potential new duplicates to prevent possible race conditions later --> <xsl:when test="count(paths/path) > 1"> <xsl:variable name="new-query"> <Item type="File" action="add" id="{@id}"> <actual_filename><xsl:value-of select="paths/path[1]" /></actual_filename> </Item> </xsl:variable> <xsl:choose> <xsl:when test="arasx:IsArasFault(arasx:CallAction('ApplyItem',$file-query))"> <Item action="add"> <xsl:copy-of select="@*" /> <xsl:copy-of select="node()" /> </Item> </xsl:when> <xsl:otherwise> <Item action="get"> <xsl:copy-of select="@*" /> <xsl:copy-of select="paths" /> </Item> </xsl:otherwise> </xsl:choose> </xsl:when> <!-- Add the file later --> <xsl:otherwise> <Item action="add"> <xsl:copy-of select="@*" /> <xsl:copy-of select="node()" /> </Item> </xsl:otherwise> </xsl:choose> </xsl:for-each> </Result> </xsl:variable>
<xsl:variable name="document-query"> <Item type="Document File" action="get" select="source_id(id),related_id(id)" where="1 = (select count(*) from innovator.DOCUMENT_FILE i where i.SOURCE_ID = [Document_File].SOURCE_ID) and 1 = (select count(*) from innovator.DOCUMENT_FILE i where i.RELATED_ID = [Document_File].RELATED_ID)"> <related_id condition="in"> <xsl:for-each select="$existing-files/Item"> <xsl:if test="position() != 1">,</xsl:if> <xsl:text>'</xsl:text> <xsl:value-of select="@id"/> <xsl:text>'</xsl:text> </xsl:for-each> </related_id> </Item> </xsl:variable>
<xsl:variable name="existing-docs" select="arasx:CallAction('ApplyItem',$document-query)//*[Item][1]" />
<Result> <xsl:for-each select="row"> <xsl:call-template name="RenderAml"> <xsl:with-param name="row" select="." /> <xsl:with-param name="existing-file" select="msxsl:node-set($unique-existing-files)/Result/Item[paths/path = current()/path]" /> <xsl:with-param name="existing-docs" select="$existing-docs" /> </xsl:call-template> </xsl:for-each> </Result>
</xsl:template>
<xsl:template name="RenderAml"> <xsl:param name="row" /> <xsl:param name="existing-file" /> <xsl:param name="existing-docs" />
<xsl:choose> <xsl:when test="$existing-file/@action = 'get'"> <xsl:variable name="existing-doc" select="$existing-docs/Item[related_id/Item/@id = $existing-file/@id]/source_id/Item" />
<xsl:choose> <xsl:when test="$existing-doc"> <Item type="Document" action="get" id="{$existing-doc/@id}"></Item> </xsl:when> <xsl:otherwise> <Item type="Document" action="add"> <Relationships> <Item type="Document File" action="add"> <related_id> <xsl:value-of select="$existing-file/@id" /> </related_id> </Item> </Relationships> </Item> </xsl:otherwise> </xsl:choose> </xsl:when> <xsl:otherwise> <Item type="Document" action="add"> <Relationships> <Item type="Document File" action="add"> <related_id> <Item type="File" action="add" id="{$existing-file/@id}"> </Item> </related_id> </Item> </Relationships> </Item> </xsl:otherwise> </xsl:choose> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>
